SCALA LUCENE DEMO

This is a simple demo of using lucene in Scala. It is a simple filesearcher
that also shows how to do simple highlighting of the search results. The demo
only works in ANSI escape code compatible terminals. The demo uses Lucene 3.1.0 
and the source code may not be valid for other versions of Lucene.

REQUIREMENTS

Terminal with ANSI escape code support
scala 2.8.1+
sbt 0.7.4+

COMPILING

Invoke sbt package in the project directory

$ sbt package

RUNNING

To find all files that has scala in its full path write:

$ sbt 'run /home/myhome/tmp scala'

AUTHOR

